<ParishCouncilLayout title="Our Monthly and Annual Meetings">
  <Hero />
  <main class="container mx-auto px-6 py-10">
    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Annual Reports</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">
          The Annual Report is published each April just before the Annual Parish Meeting which is usual held in May. It
          summarises the activities of the Parish Council for the year. At Annex A you can find the summary of the
          accounts for the financial year ending 31 March for each year.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Please click on the links below.</p>
        <div class="my-4">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">2024-25</h3>
          <ul class="my-4 list-inside list-disc">
            <li>
              <a href="/documents/2024-25/annual-report-2024-25.pdf" target="_blank">Annual Report 2024-25</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/documents/2024-25/annex-a-summary-of-accounts-2024-25.pdf" target="_blank"
                >Annex A the summary of the accounts 2024-25</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/documents/2024-25/explanation-of-variances-2024-25.pdf" target="_blank"
                >Explanation of Variances, 2024-25</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/documents/2024-25/agar-2024-25-completed.pdf" target="_blank"
                >Annual Governance and Accountability Return 2024/25 Form 2</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="my-4">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">2023-24</h3>
          <ul class="my-4 list-inside list-disc">
            <li>
              <a href="/documents/2023-24/annual-report-2023-24.pdf" target="_blank">Annual Report 2023-24</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/documents/2023-24/annex-a-summary-of-accounts-2023-24.pdf" target="_blank"
                >Annex A the summary of the accounts 2023-24</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/documents/2023-24/explanation-of-variances-2023-24.pdf" target="_blank"
                >Explanation of Variances, 2023-24</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/documents/2023-24/annual-return-form2-2023-24.pdf" target="_blank"
                >Annual Governance and Accountability Return 2023/24 Form 2</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="my-4">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">2022-23</h3>
          <ul class="my-4 list-inside list-disc">
            <li>
              <a href="/documents/2022-23/annual-report-2022-23.pdf" target="_blank">Annual Report 2022-23</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/documents/2022-23/annex-a-summary-of-accounts-2022-23.pdf" target="_blank"
                >Annex A the summary of the accounts 2022-23</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/documents/2022-23/annual-return-form2_2022-23.pdf" target="_blank"
                >Annual Governance and Accountability Return 2022/23 Form 2</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="my-4">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">2021-22</h3>
          <ul class="my-4 list-inside list-disc">
            <li>
              <a href="/documents/2021-22/annual-report-2021-22.pdf" target="_blank">Annual Report 2021-22</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="/documents/2021-22/annex-a-summary-of-accounts-2021-22.pdf" target="_blank"
